<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="KC10">
<l>payaṉaṉṟākilum pāṅkalarākilum</l>
<l>ceyal naṉṟākat tiruttip paṇikoḷvāṉ</l>
<l>kuyil niṉṟār poḻil cūḻ kurukūr nampi</l>
<l>muyalkiṉṟēṉuṉtaṉ moy kaḻaṟkaṉpaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though insignificant, even though disagreeable,</l>
<l>he rectifies [them] so that [their] conduct is good and accepts [them] as servants.</l>
<l>Lord of Kurukūr, surrounded by groves [where] cuckoos constantly coo,</l>
<l>I undertake attachment to your great ankleted feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
